---
description: Supabase schema-first workflow
globs: "supabase/**,src/api/**,src/lib/supabase/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Supabase

- All schema changes via `supabase/migrations/*.sql` — never edit prod in the dashboard
- After migrations: `supabase gen types typescript --local > src/lib/supabase/types.ts`
- Apply locally: `supabase db reset` or `supabase migration up`
- Apply remote: `supabase db push` (agent runs this, not the user)
- RLS must enforce auth server-side; client checks are UX only
